'''Kalonterium''' was an [[ore]] mined on [[Inysh]]. The [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]] strip-mined kalonterium during their rule of the planet.

It was considered a low-grade ore and was used in the production of weapons and construction materials before the advent of [[Doonium/Legends|doonium]] and [[Meleenium/Legends|meleenium]].

